Package udel.GardenProject.enums

All the different enums for the Garden Project. In retrospect, every enum in this package should've have implemented a standard interface GardenProjectEnums or something and specify a getFriendlyName() method.

Also contains other classes directly related to enums, like factory classes.
Version:
1.0
Author:
Team 0
